Package game.actions

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AttackAction
    Special Action for attacking other Actors.
    BreedAction
    Action for dinosaurs to breed with each other.
    DieAction
    Action to handle dead actors.
    DrinkAction
    Action for dinosaurs to drink water from lake.
    EatAction
    Action for dinosaurs to eat.
    ExitAction
    Action for Player to exit the current game.
    FeedAction
    Action for Player to feed a dinosaur actor.
    LayEggAction
    Action for Dinosaurs to lay an egg.
    PurchaseAction
    Action for Player to purchase items from a vending machine.
    SearchFruitAction
    Action for Player to search for fruit in Bush/Tree in same square.
